
COMMAND:
   fix 

ART:
   Fix is a command to debug your soul and some other things,
   without the need to call a wizard. Fix may help when:

   1.) You have no heartbeat
   2.) You a skill don't work
   3.) You dont know if you are allowed to wear all your armours
   4.) You have a weight bug
   5.) You want to update your legend level

   It's a good idea to type fix everytime after advancing stats or
   levels. Fix generally updates your skills.

COST:
   none 

